# Keep build context lean but KEEP everything the all-in-one root Dockerfile
# needs (web app, config/, selfhost/zzz-hackheroes-schema.sql, hh-*.sh,
# nginx.allinone.conf). The Dockerfile prunes non-web files from the served
# dir itself, so we only exclude truly unnecessary things here.
.git
.github
.DS_Store
**/.DS_Store
node_modules
allinone
# NOTE: do NOT ignore selfhost/ — the schema lives there and the build needs it.
# NOTE: .env is copied into context but pruned from the served dir by the Dockerfile.
